  body
    // start header
    header#top-bar.top-bar--light
      #top-bar__inner
        div#top-bar__logo.site-logo(href='/')
          img.img-responsive(src='img/site_logo.png', alt='demo', width='70px')
          span.logo__text(style='color:white; font-size: 22px;') Control D
        div#top-bar__navigation-toggler(href='javascript:void(0);')
          span
        #top-bar__navigation-wrap
          div
            nav#top-bar__navigation.navigation(role='navigation')
              ul
            br.hide--lg
            ul#top-bar__subnavigation
              li
                a.custom-btn.custom-btn--small.custom-btn--style-3(href='/data_share') Sharing Data
    // end header
    // start start screen
    #start-screen.start-screen--light.start-screen--style-8
      .start-screen__static-bg(style='background-image: url(img/bg_18.png);background-position: center bottom;')
        .start-screen__content
          .start-screen__content__inner
            .grid.grid--container
              .row.row--xs-center
                .col.col--md-7
                  h1.__title Sharing Data in EOS block
                  .row.col-MB-40
                    .col.col--lg-11.col--xl-9
                      .col-MB-25
                        | The plugin is supported on the EOS. Store and change data with a hash
                      .col-MB-25
                        | Share the data with companies and organization
                      .row.row--xs-center
                        .col.col--xs-auto
                          a.custom-btn.custom-btn--medium.custom-btn--style-5(style='margin-top: 20px;', href='/data_share') Data sharing center
                  .facts
                    .__inner
    // end start screen
    // start main
    main(role='main')
      // start section
      section.section
        .grid.grid--container
          .row.row--md-center
            .col.col--md-5.col--lg-6
              img.img-responsive(src='img/img_10.png', alt='demo')
            .col.hide--md.col-MB-40
            .col.col--md-7.col--lg-6
              div(data-aos='fade-left', data-aos-delay='150')
                .section-heading.col-MB-30
                  h5.__subtitle Our Vision
                  h2.__title The concept is to create a web plugin, that is supported on the EOS. 
                p.col-MB-35
                  | With the we plugin users can store (personal) data and share it for a certain period of time with for example companies and organizations. With the new AVG law it is difficult for mainly small companies to be AVG compliant. With the data box, users can easily share date for a (certain) time.
                ul.special-list
                  li.list__item.list__item--1
                    .b-table
                      .cell.v-middle
                        i.ico.fontello-lock
                      .cell.v-middle
                        h6 Store Data with a hash
                  li.list__item.list__item--2
                    .b-table
                      .cell.v-middle
                        i.ico.fontello-plane
                      .cell.v-middle
                        h6 Change Data
                  li.list__item.list__item--3
                    .b-table
                      .cell.v-middle
                        i.ico.fontello-wallet
                      .cell.v-middle
                        h6 Share Data with companies and organizations
          .col.col-MB-25  
          .col.col-MB-25  
          .row.row--md-center.row--md-reverse
            .col.col--md-5.col--lg-6
              img.img-responsive(src='img/img_11.png', alt='demo')
            .col.hide--md.col-MB-40
            .col.col--md-7.col--lg-6
              .content-grid(style='margin-left: auto;max-width: 570px;')
                div(data-aos='fade-right', data-aos-delay='150')
                  p.col-MB-35
                    | The advantage of this is that especially small companies can automatically make a link and therefore do not need to purchase large systems. They are also always AVG compliance. For the consumer it is a great advantage, because he/she has an overview of data shared with companies.
      // end section
      // end main
      // start footer
      footer#footer.text--center.text--lg-left
        .grid.grid--container
      // end footer
      #btn-to-top-wrap
        a#btn-to-top.circled(href='javascript:void(0);', data-visible-offset='800')
